citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:10-10:40am on
29-JAN-21. A voicemail on the listed number as well as several horn honks from the driveway were unanswered within
the allotted time.
End Section
